snippet.title: Bumpy's Arcade Fantasy  - 1st Level Set (1992) [PC] [MS DOS]
snippet.description:
Bumpy's Arcade Fantasy is a Puzzle game published by Loriciel in 1992.

Object of the game is to collect miscellaneous items and avoid enemies and other hazards. After all the items in the level have been collected a portal will open which will take you to the next level.

See the second level set of this game here: 
http://youtu.be/Pqv9aigye6U
